channel.title: Ipod touch help!
channel.description:
hey i got a ipod touch with wifi on it! But when i want to go on this forum i cant becaus that thing that comes when you come here for the first time. (You need to fill in yes to go to this forum) More info : I dont have flashplayer. I mean that thing if you come here for the first time : Rules you are not from JaGex etc.
Hope you understand me xD Well i just want to come on this forum with my ipod touch :(
Edit : Terms of service!

item.title: Ipod touch help!
item.dc:creator: @youridudock youridudock
item.description:
@youridudock wrote:

[quote=“Jc22493, post:5, topic:358221”][quote author=youridudock link=topic=454727.msg3330497#msg3330497 date=1283439558]

Just zoom in with your fingers and press the little box, and type in “Yes”

IF i do that it just load the terms of service again.
[/quote]
Because you’re pressing ‘enter’ on the keyboard. Type yes and press the ‘accept’ button on the page.[/quote]

Ok i will try if i am at home. Thx for all those awnsers

[/quote]

IF i do that it just load the terms of service again. :([/quote]
clear your cache and do it again and it should work
to clear your cache go into settings>safari>at bottom of page itll say “Clear Cache”
If it doesnt work after all that restart your ipod is all i can say :\
